ini]]\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} Edgar Berney<br>{{flagicon|CHE}} [[Andr\u00e9 Wicky]]\n| [[Bizzarrini Strada|Bizzarrini P538 Sport]]\n| [[Chevrolet]] 5.4L V8\n| 8\n| Steering arm<br> (3hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| S<br>5.0\n| 12\n| {{flagicon|Canada}} Comstock Racing<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} F.R. English Ltd\n| {{flagicon|AUT}} [[Jochen Rindt]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Innes Ireland]]\n| [[Ford GT40]]\n| Ford 4.7L V8\n| 8\n| Engine<br> (3hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>2.0\n| 25\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} Scuderia San Marco<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[North American Racing Team]]\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Nino Vaccarella]]<br>{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Mario Casoni]]\n| [[Dino 206 S]]\n| Ferrari 1986cc V6\n| 7\n| Water leak<br> (3hr)\n|}\n\n===Did not start===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n! Pos\n! Class\n! No\n! Team\n! Drivers\n! Chassis\n! Engine\n! Reason\n|-\n! DNS\n| P<br>1.15\n| 56\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Automobiles<br>[[Alpine (car)|Alpine]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Henri Grandsire<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Andr\u00e9 de Cortanze]]\n| [[Alpine A110]] M64\n| [[Renault]]-[[Gordini]] 1005cc S4\n| Did not start\n|-\n! DNS\n| S<br>5.0\n| 63<br>''(reserve)''\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Scuderia Bear\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Dick Holqvist<br>{{flagicon|USA}} M.R. Wylie\n| [[Ford GT40]]\n| Ford 4.7L V8\n| practice accident\n|-\n! DNA\n| P<br>5.0\n| 22\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} SpA [[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]] SEFAC\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Giancarlo Baghetti]]<br>{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Umberto Maglioli]]\n| [[Ferrari P#330 P3|Ferrari 330 P3]]\n| Ferrari 4.0L V12\n| Did not arrive\n|-\n! DNA\n| P<br>5.0\n| 23\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} Scuderia San Marco\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Louis Corbero\n| [[Scuderia Serenissima|Serenissima]] Spyder\n| Serenissima 3.5L V8\n| Did not arrive\n|-\n! DNA\n| P<br>2.0\n| 37\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} SpA [[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]] SEFAC\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} Giampiero Biscaldi<br>{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Mario Casoni]]\n| [[Dino 206 S]]\n| Ferrari 1986cc V6\n| Did not arrive\n|-\n! DNA\n| P<br>2.0\n| 39\n| {{flagic