fa Romeo\n|align=right| 3\n|-\n| 6\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Alpine\n|align=right| 1\n|}\n\n;Citations\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==References==\n* Armstrong, Douglas, English editor (1967)    ''Automobile Year #14 1966\u201367''    Lausanne: Edita S.A.\n* Clarke, R.M., editor (1997)    ''Le Mans 'The Ford and Matra Years 1966\u20131974' '' Cobham, Surrey: Brooklands Books  {{ISBN|1-85520-373-1}}\n* Clausager, Anders (1982)    ''Le Mans''    London: Arthur Barker Ltd  {{ISBN|0-213-16846-4}}\n* Fox, Charles (1973)    ''The Great Racing Cars & Drivers''    London: Octopus Books Ltd  {{ISBN|0-7064-0213-8}}\n* Laban, Brian (2001)    ''Le Mans 24 Hours''    London: Virgin Books   {{ISBN|1-85227-971-0}}\n* Moity, Christian (1974)    ''The Le Mans 24 Hour Race 1949\u20131973''    Radnor, Pennsylvania: [[Chilton Book Co]]  {{ISBN|0-8019-6290-0}}\n* Spurring, Quentin (2010)    ''Le Mans 1960\u201369''    Yeovil, Somerset: Haynes Publishing  {{ISBN|978-1-84425-584-9}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.racingsportscars.com/race/Le_Mans-1966-06-19.html  Racing Sports Cars]&nbsp;\u2013 Le Mans 24 Hours 1966 entries, results, technical detail. Retrieved 20 March 2018\n* [http://www.lemans-history.com/provas.php?ano=1966  Le Mans History]&nbsp;\u2013 Le Mans History, hour-by-hour (incl. pictures, YouTube links). Retrieved 20 March 2018\n* [http://www.wsrp.cz/wsc1966.html#7  World Sports Racing Prototypes]&nbsp;\u2013 results, reserve entries & chassis numbers. Retrieved 20 March 2018\n* [http://www.teamdan.com/archive/wsc/1966/66lemans.html  Team Dan]&nbsp;\u2013 results & reserve entries, explaining driver listings. Retrieved 20 March 2018\n* [http://www.uniquecarsandparts.com.au/le_mans_1966  Unique Cars & Parts]&nbsp;\u2013 results & reserve entries. Retrieved 20 March 2018\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170705000830/http://www.formula2.net/1966.htm  Formula 2]&nbsp;\u2013 Le Mans results & reserve entries. Retrieved 20 March 2018\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7rrVOVuwPV0 YouTu